popt4jlib.GA

Class DGAIndividualPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • popt4jlib.GA.DGAIndividualPool

  • class DGAIndividualPool
extends java.lang.Object
    The class is responsible for maintaining a sufficiently large array of DGAIndividual objects, and there will be a pool for each thread of execution. In this way, there will be no need for invoking the new operator within the running threads requiring such objects, unless a thread at some point runs out of space in its thread-local pool.

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java
